/articles/CBMinwFBVV95cUxNeUItMk5wLVlEaWxhNjlsemhWZHF5MzIxRXl5QVo3HlPdFVnMDRMRldTYmQyWXkyWlpvWlBpeEVxSnlJZmp0aVFmaTdOMURVTlRBWWQwSGJicmo2R0t2ZzR6czFybnE2Z2tBbUFDVUtmNTgwMjNiNmZDZWNxajRpMEJEZ2xpSTlPV2lwaGN5bjNMbmJkOUVOc2lsRmMxVnc?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">Times Opinion: Trump is losing his war on offshore wind power - Chattanooga Times Free Press</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">Invenergy to terminate four offshore wind leases under US settlement agreement - Windtech International</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </li>\n            </ul>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n            <b>5. 글로벌 해상풍력 시장의 확장과 도전 과제</b>\n            <ul>\n                <li>독일 해상풍력 시장은 CfD(차액결제계약) 기반의 새로운 경매 시스템 도입 요구 등 정책적 불확실성을 겪고 있습니다. 하지만 아마존과 같은 글로벌 기업의 대규모 전력 구매 계약은 여전히 해상풍력 시장의 성장 잠재력을 보여줍니다. 한편, 어업 공동체와의 갈등은 해상풍력 개발이 전 세계적으로 직면한 공통적인 사회적 도전 과제임을 시사합니다.</li>\n                <li>관련 기사:\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMixAFBVV95cUxPRDBEQlZERmhFajNFSGFvNnpTTGNsd29fay16RF9OSGNxcHZobF9FYW85c2hEUzA3UTl4cU9mMDNSNl9IQndCQmJnLUs4Yk94MWhzSS1DRnlmc2dyYVExQ3g1OUdxMDlEcDZ6UFBPRW1VRnRLcWdIVERJdV9xRHM5THQzWTJoMVhRRDdJZWh1Nm82TlFiNktaOE9iODNQZnlSNTByOVVmN05RNDNBNVMxSFJQSzJPQVdBZHE5dzB5OF8tVTFO?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">Pressure mounts for new CfD-backed auctions amid German offshore wind uncertainty - Wind Power Monthly</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiuwFBVV95cUxORm1KTUpYamY3VVpmaElGS2pEUnZBMkN1VHkzbERDaHFPdDJaMkUxTlBSME1WaUQ5UTU2YlV6Z185a0d3MGV2ckFNendqVDNCQ2xWNEdxT3FKMEx5NGM0ZGNObHp3VGVzZlBmVi0yQkxHSHNQTDA3STZzMEN4eUMxV0paTDEzcnVlRFBCTS15Sm5KU3VJQ1I1X0lCZ3BxU0lrczBvS3Jhc3otVmxjeGhKM2lNcmZSemdFNWNr?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">Amazon strikes 'record power deal' for German offshore wind farm - Recharge News</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMigAFB